text: 510-516 Ohio Street is a historic commercial building located at Terre Haute, Vigo County, Indiana. It was built in 1891–1892, and is a three-story, rectangular, Italianate style brick building. It features stone, cast iron, and pressed metal decorative elements. It was renovated in 1975.
